Num Annotation for IntType or RealType parameters.
 

Package com.netcracker.tc.types.standard.num Description

Integer and real scenario parameter types. IntType is inferred for fields and params of int or Integer type. RealType is inferred for fields and params of double or Double type. Use annotation Num.min() and Num.max() to set bounds.
